section(class="template-wrapper self_3")
    aside(class="template-asideLeft o-aside-Item")
    |
    |
    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content")
            h5 Listen to the following report about New Zealand and how government introduces graphic warnings on cigarettes.
            div(class="row mt30 row-flex align-items-center")
                .col.xs12.md9.ta-c.col-center
                    audio(controls class='mt30 row')
                        source(src='unit_1/module_2/assets/audios/self_3_1.mp3' type='audio/mpeg')
                        | Your browser does not support the audio element.
                    div(class="row")
                        .c-cardGreen
                            .c-cardGreenContent
                                h6 Set A health warnings - cigarette packs
                                p Read the full story here:
                                p #[a(href="http://www.health.gov.au/internet/main/publishing.nsf/content/tobacco-warn-A" target="blank" style="word-break:break-all") http://www.health.gov.au/internet/main/publishing.nsf/content/tobacco-warn-A]

            div(class="row row-flex mt30")
                h5 Answer the following questions based on the audio recording.
                div(class="row mt30")
                    .col.xs12.md6
                        div(class="row")
                            h6 #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] The new pictures will…
                            .row
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_1" value="1")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_1") Replace all writing on the cigarette boxes as they are more graphic.
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_2" value="2")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_2") Will replace the cigarette boxes.
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_1" id="selInput_3" value="3")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_3") Will leave only 10% of the space on the back of the box.
                                input(type="hidden" ng-model="valorinputa" class="js-select")
                        |
                        div(class="row mt20")
                            h6 #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Complete the sentence.
                            p #[input(type="text" class="c-input js-escribir")] need to have the new boxes on their shelf 2008.
                        |
                        div(class="row mt20")
                            h6 #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Fill in the blank space with appropriate person.
                            p According to #[input(type="text" class="c-input" ng-model="completeOra" readonly)] “Pictures were more effective than written warnings”.
                            .row
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_4" ng-click="completeOra = 'the ex-prime minister' " value="1")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_4") the ex-prime minister
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_5" ng-click="completeOra = 'a former smoker' " value="2")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_5") a former smoker
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_2" id="selInput_6" ng-click="completeOra = 'the retailer' " value="3")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_6") the retailer
                                input(type="hidden" ng-model="valorinputb" class="js-select")
                    |
                    .col.xs12.md6
                        div(class="row")
                            h6 #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Answer true or false
                            p There are 14 warning pictures initially and 7 to come later.
                            div(class="row row-flex justify-around")
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_7" value="1")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox xs12 sm5" for="selInput_7") True.
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_3" id="selInput_8" value="2")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox xs12 sm5" for="selInput_8") False.
                                input(type="hidden" ng-model="valorinputc" class="js-select")
                        |
                        div(class="row mt30")
                            h6 #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] When corrections need to be made to labeling the minister of health says…
                            div(class="row")
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_9" value="1")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_9") They will consult an all changes.
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_10" value="2")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_10") They will assist with the payments.
                                input(type="radio" class="c-inputRadio" name="sel_input_4" id="selInput_11" value="3")
                                label(class="c-Checkbox row ta-l " for="selInput_11") Companies need to pay for them themselves.
                                input(type="hidden" ng-model="valorinputd" class="js-select")
    |
    |
    aside(class="template-asideRight o-aside-Item")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconRefresh" ng-click="reloadEscribSelect()")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconCheck" ng-click="CompTxt_SelectMult()")
